title: 3 and Out - Cousins Can't; Pats' Survival Instinct; Niners' Chemistry; Cowboys Face Reality; Baker's Broken; Michael Thomas Dominance; Week 16 Recap
itunes:title: 3 and Out - Cousins Can't; Pats' Survival Instinct; Niners' Chemistry; Cowboys Face Reality; Baker's Broken; Michael Thomas Dominance; Week 16 Recap
description:
In this episode, Middlekauff reacts to the Packers MNF win over the Vikings, Kirk Cousins continued awfulness in big games; the Packers dominant defensive performance, why even a down New England is still a playoff threat, why the Cowboys are paying the price for not moving on from Jason Garrett last year. He also gives his biggest takeaways from a packed Week 16. Follow John on twitter @JohnMiddlekauff and go to theherdnow.com to find the latest content. Subscribe now!
